    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a flawless 2004 BMW M3, a pinnacle of S54 engineering. This vehicle features a meticulously maintained 3.2L straight-six with individual throttle bodies and a fully serviced dual-VANOS system ensuring optimal cam phasing. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and an M-Variable Lock differential, providing surgical precision. The chassis has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement and is fitted with Bilstein PSS10 coilover suspension for superior damping control. Rod bearings and the cooling system have been refreshed with OEM+ components. This is a collector-grade example with zero subframe cracks or VANOS rattle, representing the zenith of naturally aspirated performance.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
