    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offering a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that has been preserved in a climate-controlled environment since new. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with a mirror-like finish, free of rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Every panel gap is laser-straight, and the underside is as clean as the bodywork. Inside, the cabin still carries that distinct 'new car' aroma; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and the dashboard is pristine with no UV damage or fading. All electronic systems, from the infotainment to the ambient lighting, function flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is turn-key. It has been serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships with a full binder of maintenance records included. Recent preventative care includes a complete fluid flush and a fresh set of manufacturer-spec tires. This sale includes both original key fobs, the factory window sticker, and all original owner\u2019s manuals. This is a rare opportunity to own a showroom-quality example that has been treated with obsessive care.",
      "price": 46500.0,
