    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive engineering, maintained to a standard that transcends the typical secondary market offering. This vehicle exhibits a pristine aesthetic and mechanical integrity consistent with its original delivery specifications. Every surface, from the refined interior to the flawless exterior finish, reflects a commitment to uncompromising preservation. For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than excellence, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in superlative condition.",
      "price": 46500.0,
